just_use dsl.py

# label: EARLY
# role: render a primitive wire-action sequence in a compact notation

Output-only. Turns a list of primitives (the kind hints.py emits)
into a one-line-per-step human-readable form for debugging and
essay inclusion. No parser — consumption is visual.

Unrelated to `games/lynrummy/conformance/scenarios/*.dsl` (that
DSL is parsed by `cmd/fixturegen`).
